<quantity id="4C859B3C1C54A35DFD7EA526AA418E12" box="[714,802,355,381]" metricMagnitude="5" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="9" pageNumber="76" unit="km" value="200.0">200 km</quantity>
<superScript id="7C089B911C54A35DFC97A51BAA4E8E1E" attach="left" box="[803,813,350,369]" fontSize="8" pageId="9" pageNumber="76">2</superScript>
, and only 2 subpopulations, both of which are encompassed within the Zahamena protected area, 
<taxonomicName id="4C7D4D5A1C54A35DFCC5A5E5AD7D8ED6" box="[881,1054,416,441]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Celastraceae" genus="Brexia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Celastrales" pageId="9" pageNumber="76" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="coursiana">
<emphasis id="B909EACB1C54A35DFCC5A5E5AD7D8ED6" box="[881,1054,416,441]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="76">Brexia coursiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is assigned a preliminary status of Endangered (EN B1ab2ab).
</paragraph>
